    <item>
      <title>印度最高法院要求 Sebi 在三个月内结束阿达尼调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/top-india-court-asks-sebi-to-close-adani-probe-in-three-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院命令市场监管机构在三个月内完成对阿达尼集团的调查，并表示不再需要进行更多调查，这可能会为这家印度企业集团遭受卖空者攻击引发的长达一年的传奇画上句号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/top-india-court-asks-sebi-to-close-adani-probe-in-three-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度卡车司机在与莫迪政府会谈后取消罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/india-truckers-call-off-strike-after-talks-with-modi-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度卡车和公共汽车运营商工会要求成员结束为期两天的罢工，此前总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府向他们保证，只有在协商后才会对肇事逃逸案件实施新的处罚措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/india-truckers-call-off-strike-after-talks-with-modi-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>轴心银行：印度的积极惊喜将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-03/axis-bank-india-s-positive-surprises-will-continue-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axis 银行首席经济学家兼 Axis Capital 全球研究主管尼尔坎特·米什拉 (Neelkanth Mishra) 表示，积极的惊喜将继续出现，迫使趋势增长假设上调，并引发印度 GDP 预测的上调。他与 Rishaad Salamat 就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-03/axis-bank-india-s-positive-surprises-will-continue-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
